HEADWORD: Synchrony
<hw>Syn"chro*ny</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The concurrence of
events in time; synchronism.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Geological contemporaneity is the same as chronological
<qex>synchrony</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Huxley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Synchysis</ent>⟦br⟧
